channel.title: Bucket not filling but fading out? Rectangular fading out?
channel.description:
[img]http://img159.imageshack.us/img159/3968/wtfja8.png[/img]
For example, when I make a screenshot and use the rectangular on it and copy it it will fade out like you see on the screenshot. Also the rectangular doesn't have sharp corners anymore but a little bit round. When I use rectangular and want to fill it with something such as the bucket, or a pencil, it will not fill completely, but it will fade out like on the screenshot.
